long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Flying Triangle is an arcade game where we move forward with a flying triangle without hitting the obstacles.

There is a triangle that moves by passing in the game. We can control this triangle. With the triangle we can control, we proceed by paying attention to the obstacles we encounter. We earn points by progressing carefully. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Flying Triangle has emerged as a skill game designed for us who love children's games, as it is fun and challenging.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Flying Triangle game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
